{"tid":557063,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"本來年尾想一家人齊齊整整，宜家比個基督徒巴士兇手拆散！","createTime":"2018-02-11T04:20:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-11T14:56:00.000Z","uid":65346,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"64be39cbfb2b2a1a7f6f4e359adc2ff6ea350d7d","tid":557063,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T04:20:41.000Z","msg":"無人1性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"285441be3d29ca083b5a8c2440c96377da24e6e9","tid":557063,"uid":53666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T04:33:26.000Z","msg":"節哀"},{"pid":"b42dc7d1f9a634b97002ba244c2dd1b469867ef8","tid":557063,"uid":43575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T04:36:04.000Z","msg":"所有野都係因果循環，善哉善哉"},{"pid":"d4fed76c12b58983a6a9f30a7b95d8fb0e56a006","tid":557063,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T04:51:10.000Z","msg":"基督賤種"},{"pid":"7871425bab3be1328e7669d5ebba6872f55eb1db","tid":557063,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T14:56:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180211/57820119\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180211%2F57820119&d=4YjHC32Alak4kEUk3d%2FSJROFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=50ec52b2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180211%2F57820119&h=86bb6e4d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180211/57820119</a><br />\n<br />\n車禍19名死者之一的黃國安（60歲）是退休公務員，原定一家四口約好了外家在年廿八蒸糕團年，居於元朗村屋的岳母昨今晨還在準備材料，豈料突然收到女兒告知噩耗，不禁老淚縱橫，她哽咽說：「我好心痛，佢好好人，好孝順！」<br />\n<br />\n黃國安是元朗沙埔村原居民，與妻育有兩名女兒，分別就讀大學及中學，一家四口住在大埔林村。據知他原任職運輸署高級技術主任，2015年曾獲授予公務員事務局局長嘉許狀，肯定其工作表現，他數個月前正式退休，上月23日度過60歲生日，一早計劃好與妻子如何享受退休生活，可惜昨晚遇車禍不幸離世。<br />\n居於元朗的岳母稱讚這位女婿十分孝順，原本約好了年廿八一家人蒸糕團年，她今日一早還在準備材料，突然接獲通知稱女婿遇車禍罹難，家人下午趕到現場路祭，其間她不禁哽咽：「我好痛苦，今朝喊咗一大餐！」目前由其他子女代為打點後事，至於女兒一家人日後生活問題，現時只有見步行步。"}]}